import React from 'react' import PropTypes from 'prop-types' import './cta.css' const CTA = (props) => (
{props.heading1}

{props.content1}

{props.action1}
) CTA.defaultProps = { heading1: 'Custom creations. Made for you.', content1: 'MadeforMe connects you with talented makers who bring your custom ideas to life — one-of-a-kind items made just for you.', action1: 'Post a Request', } CTA.propTypes = { heading1: PropTypes.string, content1: PropTypes.string, action1: PropTypes.string, } export default CTA
